    Our Story 

    THE PASSION FOR PIZZA

    Rustique Pizza is a family run pizza restaurant offering award winning stone oven pizza, homemade bread, and familiar Italian dishes in a comfortable, friendly and fun atmosphere. We will also meet the needs of our customers by offering efficient delivery and take out service. Our cheese, bread and desserts are all made on the premises.
